# Ad-hoc analysis scratch (kept local, not committed)
# Background-agent audits drop output at the project root; we sweep
# them into _ai_notes/ before commit. The patterns below catch the
# ones we've seen so they don't slip into a commit accidentally.
_ai_notes/
*_AUDIT.md
*_AUDIT_*.md
*_AUDIT.txt
*_AUDIT_*.txt
*_SUMMARY.md
*_SUMMARY.txt
*_REPORT.md
*_FIXES.md
AUDIT_*.md
AUDIT_*.txt
DESIGN_TOKENS_*.md
DESIGN_TOKENS_*.txt
DESIGN_TOKEN_*.md
DESIGN_SYSTEM_*.md
DARK_MODE_*.md
DARK_MODE_*.txt
IMAGE_ANALYSIS_*.md
IMAGE_RENDERING_*.md
IMAGE_RENDERING_*.txt
PERFORMANCE_*.md
PERFORMANCE_*.txt
UI_*.md
EXPLORATION_*.md
